|               |   SortExec: TopK(fetch=10), expr=[l_linenumber@2 DESC], preserve_partitioning=[false]                         |
|               |     ProjectionExec: expr=[l_comment@0 as l_comment, l_partkey@2 as l_partkey, l_linenumber@1 as l_linenumber] |
|               |       BytesProcessedExec                                                                                      |
|               |         MongoDBExec projection=[l_comment, l_linenumber, l_partkey] filters=[{}]                              |
|               |                                                                                                               |
